Interesting idea, but I personally do not want to be a buffer of any sort. That's what healers are for. <P>Adding utility spells does not address our core problems of lacking comparable CC, survivability, and peT issues.<P>Anything we gain will only count against us when, if ever, this class get reviewed for viability. Need to address the "Core" issues of the class in terms of providing the realm with what we were initially designed to do. <P>All my own opinion of course.
