<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Agreed, the core issues are our survivability, and our capability at CC.  First we have to make us on par with our counterparts; then we can address the role of "Primary Mezzers" and *all* of them getting some sort of compensation for having the tool they were built upon fundamentally ripped out from under them.<P>Everyone says that Sorcerers have weaker defense because we traded it for offense.  However, they fail to realize that a CC-Based Sorcerer (Mind Spec) will *not* have that offense they speak of, and thus are instead merely gimped by their poor defense.  So whatever defense-boosters are added to Mind, they need to be added high up there so that, indeed, people can't get the armor of the other Mezzers yet retain the offense that we've found in High Body Spec.
</FONT>
