My idea is I believe realistic and less of a hassle to implement .<P>1) Remove charm from the mind spec and increase the sorcerer's spec points to 1.5x or 2x<P>2)Change the Body Spec DD to a lesser resisted line and increase the range of the Matter DD to bring both into line with other secondary nukes.<P>The  Sorcerer will loose one of it's most recognizable skills , but that was the case the minuet that Mythic chose to give Minstrels a Charm.<P>This will help considerably with the current lack of a Primary AOE CC class in Albion PVE.<P>Being able to survive will encrease with personal damage output.<P>--------------------<P>Dravenangel<BR>50th Sorcerer <BR>Morgan le Fey
