Neptonius(35 Sorcerer Bors): Sorcerers need a high spec lvl CC option, ie. CC spell of some use past 34mind spec. Perhaps bolt range on our 44 mez, but I do not think more instas is a good idea.  Also for survivability, a PBAoE DD in our Mind line would be an indirect but effective way to increase survivability without making us too overpowered.  I want to play my class as it was intended, not as a mini-wiz to farm rp's. If I wanted to be a nuker I would have rolled a wiz, but I am already at 35 falling behind the curve of other realms CCers.
